>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e878a96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Definitions<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Multiple Organ Dysfunction Syndrome (MODS)<\/em>: Development of Potentially Reversible Physiologic Derangements Involving \u2265 2 Organ Systems Not Directly Involved in the Primary Disorder Causing ICU Admission<ul><li><em>Multiple Organ Failure (MOF)<\/em> \u2013 Older Term Indicating Complete Organ Failure (No Longer Used)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Classification:<ul><li><em>Primary MODS<\/em> \u2013 Organ Dysfunction Directly Caused by an Insult Itself<\/li><li><em>Secondary MODS <\/em>\u2013 Organ Dysfunction Caused by the Host Response to an Insult<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Causes<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Infection (Sepsis &amp; Septic Shock)<\/li><li>Systemic Inflammatory Response Syndrome (SIRS)<ul><li>Pancreatitis<\/li><li>Aspiration<\/li><li>Ischemia-Reperfusion Injury<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Major Trauma or Burns<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Common Dysfunctions<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS)<\/li><li>Cardiomyopathy &amp; Heart Failure<\/li><li>Acute Kidney Injury (AKI)<\/li><li>Encephalopathy<\/li><li>Liver Dysfunction<\/li><li>Disseminated Intravascular Coagulation (DIC)<\/li><li>Coagulopathy<\/li><li>Bone Marrow Suppression<\/li><li>Stress Ulceration<\/li><li>Paralytic Ileus<\/li><li>Intestinal Ischemia<\/li><li>Pancreatitis<\/li><li>Acalculous Cholecystitis<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Post-Traumatic Pattern<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Risk Factors:<ul><li>Early Dysfunction: <strong>Shock<\/strong><\/li><li>Late Dysfunction: <strong>Infection<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Patterns of Dysfunction:<ul><li>Early Dysfunction: <strong>Pulmonary &amp; Cardiac Failure<\/strong><\/li><li>Late Dysfunction: Pulmonary &amp; <strong>Hepatic<\/strong> Failure<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Prognosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Associated with High Mortality Rates<\/li><li>0 Failing Organ Systems: &lt; 10%<\/li><li>1 Failing Organ Systems: 0-30%<\/li><li>2 Failing Organ Systems: 20-50%<\/li><li>3 Failing Organ Systems: 40-80%<\/li><li>4 Failing Organ Systems: 60-100%<\/li><li>\u2265 5 Failing Organ Systems: 80-100%<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d0f50d3 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d0f50d3\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5c15760\" data-id=\"5c15760\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ca1fb0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8ca1fb0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Multiple Organ Dysfunction (MOD) Score<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Predicts Prognosis in Patients with MODS<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\